  "title": "Physiotherapist",
  "description": "<p>We are on the lookout for an experienced Physiotherapist to provide exceptional care to our clients. With 11 outlets across Singapore and growing operations in Malaysia and Indonesia, we offer private space for helping clients achieve their fitness and rehabilitation goals in a professional and supportive environment.</p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>- Assess, diagnose, and treat clients with physical injuries and conditions.</p>\n<p>- Develop and implement individualized treatment plans to restore mobility and function.</p>\n<p>- Educate clients on prevention and self-care strategies.</p>\n<p>- Maintain equipment and ensure a safe workout environment.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>- Degree in Physiotherapy and registration with a relevant professional body.</p>\n<p>- Minimum 2 years of clinical experience preferred.</p>\n<p>- Strong diagnostic and treatment skills.</p>\n<p>- Excellent interpersonal and communication abilities.</p>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p>\n<p>- Competitive remuneration and incentives<br>\n- Staff discount</p>\n<p>- Collaborative and supportive work environment</p>",
